div.p: Security controls that are in place for the entire organization.

ul.li: Every employee must use MFA with the cloud tenant.
There is a process for creation/destruction of accounts.
From which corporate network(s) can employees access the cloud tenant?

div.p: Security controls that address the security of project-specific code.

ul.li: Do project dependencies undergo routine CVE scanning?
Does source code undergo routine SAST scanning?
Are unit tests for the source code ran regularly?

div.p: Security controls for infrastructure provisioned specifically for a project.

ul.li: Does the storage solution implement backups?
Does the storage solution implement access control?
Are project data encrypted at rest?
